---
const highlights = [
  { value: "3+", label: "Years Experience" },
  { value: "15+", label: "Projects Delivered" },
  { value: "20+", label: "Technologies" },
];
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="section-container">
    <span class="section-label">01 â€” About</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading">About Me</h2>
    <p class="section-subheading">A bit about my background and what drives me.</p>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-5 text-surface-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        <p>
          I'm a <strong class="text-white font-semibold">multidisciplinary technical professional</strong> with
          expertise in workflow automation, data engineering, and digital
          operations. I specialize in <strong class="text-white font-semibold">no-code/low-code platforms</strong> like
          n8n and Zapier, API integrations, and process optimization.
        </p>
        <p>
          My day-to-day involves building automated systems, designing
          <strong class="text-white font-semibold">ETL pipelines</strong> with tools like Apache Airflow and dbt, and
          writing Python to solve real business problems. I've eliminated
          manual workloads, <strong class="text-white font-semibold">replaced entire VA teams with automation</strong>,
          and helped businesses achieve 24/7 operational continuity.
        </p>
        <p>
          I hold a <strong class="text-white font-semibold">BS in Computer Science (Cum Laude)</strong> from Mindanao
          State University, where I was awarded Best in Thesis and Programmer
          of the Year. I've also taught programming, data structures, and
          databases as a Computer Science Instructor.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-4">
        {
          highlights.map((item) => (
            <div class="glass-card p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-400 mb-1 tracking-tight">
                {item.value}
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm text-surface-400">{item.label}</div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
